#. <section class="sutta" id="an4.147"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.147:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.147:0.2"
msgid "15. Ābhāvagga"
msgstr "15. Brightness"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an4.147:0.3"
msgid "147. Dutiyakālasutta"
msgstr "147. Times (2nd)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an4.147:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Cattārome, bhikkhave, kālā sammā bhāviyamānā sammā anuparivattiyamānā "
"anupubbena āsavānaṃ khayaṃ pāpenti."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, when these four times are rightly developed and progressed, "
"they gradually lead to the ending of defilements."

msgctxt "an4.147:1.2"
msgid "Katame cattāro?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "an4.147:1.3"
msgid ""
"Kālena dhammassavanaṃ, kālena dhammasākacchā, kālena sammasanā, kālena "
"vipassanā—"
msgstr ""
"A time for listening to the teaching, a time for discussing the teaching, a "
"time for serenity, and a time for discernment."

msgctxt "an4.147:1.4"
msgid ""
"ime kho, bhikkhave, cattāro kālā sammā bhāviyamānā sammā anuparivattiyamānā "
"anupubbena āsavānaṃ khayaṃ pāpenti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
#. VAR: samuddaṃ → samuddaṃ sāgaraṃ (bj, pts1, mr) | samuddasāgaraṃ (s1-3, km)
msgctxt "an4.147:2.1"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, uparipabbate thullaphusitake deve vassante taṃ udakaṃ "
"yathāninnaṃ pavattamānaṃ pabbatakandarapadarasākhā paripūreti; "
"pabbatakandarapadarasākhā paripūrā kusobbhe paripūrenti; kusobbhā paripūrā "
"mahāsobbhe paripūrenti; mahāsobbhā paripūrā kunnadiyo paripūrenti; kunnadiyo "
"paripūrā mahānadiyo paripūrenti; mahānadiyo paripūrā samuddaṃ paripūrenti."
msgstr ""
"It’s like when it rains heavily on a mountain top, and the water flows "
"downhill to fill the hollows, crevices, and creeks. As they become full, "
"they fill up the pools. The pools fill up the lakes, the lakes fill up the "
"streams, and the streams fill up the rivers. And as the rivers become full, "
"they fill up the ocean."

msgctxt "an4.147:2.2"
msgid ""
"Evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, ime cattāro kālā sammā bhāviyamānā sammā "
"anuparivattiyamānā anupubbena āsavānaṃ khayaṃ pāpentī”ti."
msgstr ""
"In the same way, when these four times are rightly developed and progressed, "
"they gradually lead to the ending of defilements.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.147:2.3"
msgid "Sattamaṃ."
msgstr ""
